overview.en: acBTC is a composite asset backed by a basket of ERC20 BTC. The acBTC ecosystem integrates native BTC and ERC20 BTC, with swap, lending and yield generating applications into one highly secure, efficient and usable standard.
overview.zh: acBTC 是由一篮子ERC20 BTC 支持的合成资产。acBTC 生态系统是一组针对原生BTC 与ERC20 BTC 设计，集兑换、稳定币和生息应用于一身的协议。acBTC 是以安全、高效和可用为设计目标。
